@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mttycr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v2 + 0.42 * v1 + 0.84)))
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = wp.cos(v1)
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.23) - (tmp + 0.16 / tmp + 0.61)) / v2)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.43)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.32)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.52 - tmp + 0.38)))
    data[tid] = v0
